on behalf of the entire canucks organization we would like to thank steve for his many contributions to our club as a player and manager over nearly 20 years since his days as a player and continuing through his time spent in our front office steve was a committed member of our team and community this is an opportunity that steve could not pass up and we are in full support of his decision to advance his career we wish him his wife denise and their entire family the best of luck in the future
